description:
Philippines Mission Trip 2018 - In March of 2018, a White Horse Media-sponsored group of 28 individuals, primarily from churches in Washington and Idaho, conducted eleven evangelistic meetings in the Philippines. Amazing things happened! Through Gods power and blessing, over 300 precious people were baptized. The 4+ minute video shows some of what happened. May our Lord Jesus Christ be praised!
